      <item>
        <title>My favorite sublime plugins</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/images/2016-09-10-my-sublime.png&quot; alt=&quot;That is as my sublime looks like&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;the-list-of-my-favorite-sublime-text-3-plugins&quot;&gt;The list of my favorite sublime text 3 plugins&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;AngularJS - better angular support&lt;/li&gt;
